dct_title_s: GIS data of the Monterey Bay
dct_description_sm: A compilation of data and imagery of the Monterey Bay area, including coastline, imagery, and bathymetry.
"Registered to the WGS84 horizontal datum"--Back of container.
"Compiled by Gerry Hatcher ... [et al.]"--Back of container.

System requirements: Computer ; text editor or word processing program; image-display software capable of displaying TIFF images of at least 5 MB in size; computer display supporting 256 or more colors; ISO 9660-compatable CD-ROM drive.  Recommended software: ARCView GIS with Spatial Analyst Extension, ARC/INFO, or ArcExplorer (the latter included on the disc, requires Windows 95 or NT and at least 15 MB hard disk space)
